#: 01_02N01
msgctxt "01_02N01"
msgid "I will personally see that it is on the next plane."
msgstr "I will personally see that it is on the next plane."

#: 01_03P01
msgctxt "01_03P01"
msgid "Eh, perhaps not."
msgstr "Eh, perhaps not."

#: 01_04P01
msgctxt "01_04P01"
msgid "I see."
msgstr "I see."

#: 01_09N01
msgctxt "01_09N01"
msgid "Help a poor soul."
msgstr "Help a poor soul."

#: 01_09N02
msgctxt "01_09N02"
msgid "Help a poor soul."
msgstr "Help a poor soul."

#: 01_09N03
msgctxt "01_09N03"
msgid "Help a poor soul."
msgstr "Help a poor soul."

#: 01_09N04
msgctxt "01_09N04"
msgid "Help a poor soul."
msgstr "Help a poor soul."

#: 01_09N05
msgctxt "01_09N05"
msgid "Help a poor soul."
msgstr "Help a poor soul."

#: 01_09P01
msgctxt "01_09P01"
msgid "Do you speak English?"
msgstr "Do you speak English?"

#: 01_09P02
msgctxt "01_09P02"
msgid "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"
msgstr "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"

#: 01_09P03
msgctxt "01_09P03"
msgid "Are you the blacksmith?"
msgstr "Are you the blacksmith?"

#: 01_09P04
msgctxt "01_09P04"
msgid "Do you know when the blacksmith opens?"
msgstr "Do you know when the blacksmith opens?"

#: 01_09P05
msgctxt "01_09P05"
msgid "I don't suppose you have a pass to get through that archway at the end of the street, do you?"
msgstr "I don't suppose you have a pass to get through that archway at the end of the street, do you?"

#: 01_09P06
msgctxt "01_09P06"
msgid "That old amulet. Could I buy it?"
msgstr "That old amulet. Could I buy it?"

#: 01_09P07
msgctxt "01_09P07"
msgid "Perhaps I'll talk to you later, if I may."
msgstr "Perhaps I'll talk to you later, if I may."

#: 01_10P01
msgctxt "01_10P01"
msgid "It was worth a try."
msgstr "It was worth a try."

#: 02_02P01
msgctxt "02_02P01"
msgid "What a beautiful day!"
msgstr "What a beautiful day!"

#: 02_02P02
msgctxt "02_02P02"
msgid "Do you speak English?"
msgstr "Do you speak English?"

#: 02_02P03
msgctxt "02_02P03"
msgid "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"
msgstr "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"

#: 02_03P04
msgctxt "02_03P04"
msgid "May I ask how you came by that helmet, madam?"
msgstr "May I ask how you came by that helmet, madam?"

#: 02N01
msgctxt "02N01"
msgid "You must have a pass."
msgstr "You must have a pass."

#: 03_02N01
msgctxt "03_02N01"
msgid "You must have a pass."
msgstr "You must have a pass."

#: 03_02N02
msgctxt "03_02N02"
msgid "I do not have passes. I examine passes."
msgstr "I do not have passes. I examine passes."

#: 03_02P01
msgctxt "03_02P01"
msgid "I'd like to go through there."
msgstr "I'd like to go through there."

#: 03_02P02
msgctxt "03_02P02"
msgid "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"
msgstr "You don't happen to have a pass to the Hall of Classics, do you?"

#: 03_03P01
msgctxt "03_03P01"
msgid "And a fine job you're doing, too."
msgstr "And a fine job you're doing, too."

#: 03_06N02
msgctxt "03_06N02"
msgid "Through there."
msgstr "Through there."

#: 03_06P02
msgctxt "03_06P02"
msgid "Where do I get a pass?"
msgstr "Where do I get a pass?"

#: 03_07P03
msgctxt "03_07P03"
msgid "Thanks. I couldn't believe that's what you said. I needed to hear it again."
msgstr "Thanks. I couldn't believe that's what you said. I needed to hear it again."

#: 04_01N01
msgctxt "04_01N01"
msgid "And now, Mr. Ripley. Where will you be traveling?"
msgstr "And now, Mr. Ripley. Where will you be traveling?"

#: 04_01N05
msgctxt "04_01N05"
msgid "Goodbye, Mr. Ripley. Goodbye, Mi-chan."
msgstr "Goodbye, Mr. Ripley. Goodbye, Mi-chan."

#: 04_01N06
msgctxt "04_01N06"
msgid "See you again, Mr. Ripley."
msgstr "See you again, Mr. Ripley."

#: 04_01P01
msgctxt "04_01P01"
msgid "I'd like to book passage."
msgstr "I'd like to book passage."

#: 04_01P02
msgctxt "04_01P02"
msgid "I'd like to send a parcel to New York."
msgstr "I'd like to send a parcel to New York."

#: 04_01P03
msgctxt "04_01P03"
msgid "I'd like to withdraw the money in my account."
msgstr "I'd like to withdraw the money in my account."

#: 04_01P04
msgctxt "04_01P04"
msgid "I'd like to buy some yuan."
msgstr "I'd like to buy some yuan."

#: 04_01P05
msgctxt "04_01P05"
msgid "Thanks, Qian Shu! Goodbye!"
msgstr "Thanks, Qian Shu! Goodbye!"

#: 04_02N01
msgctxt "04_02N01"
msgid "I will personally see that it is on the next plane."
msgstr "I will personally see that it is on the next plane."

#: 04_03N01
msgctxt "04_03N01"
msgid "Thank you, Mr. Ripley. Please sign here."
msgstr "Thank you, Mr. Ripley. Please sign here."

#: 04_04N01
msgctxt "04_04N01"
msgid "I'm sorry Mr. Ripley, your account is empty."
msgstr "I'm sorry Mr. Ripley, your account is empty."

#: 04_06N01
msgctxt "04_06N01"
msgid "And now, Mr. Ripley, when will you be ready to leave?"
msgstr "And now, Mr. Ripley, when will you be ready to leave?"

#: 04_06P01
msgctxt "04_06P01"
msgid "New York."
msgstr "New York."

#: 04_07P02
msgctxt "04_07P02"
msgid "Danzig."
msgstr "Danzig."

#: 04_08P03
msgctxt "04_08P03"
msgid "SIKIM"
msgstr "SIKIM"

#: 04_08P04
msgctxt "04_08P04"
msgid "Peru."
msgstr "Peru."

#: 04_09P01
msgctxt "04_09P01"
msgid "NOW!"
msgstr "NOW!"

#: 04_09P02
msgctxt "04_09P02"
msgid "I'll let you know."
msgstr "I'll let you know."

#: 04_11N01
msgctxt "04_11N01"
msgid "Huh, Mr. Ripley, I cannot find any money in your account. Could pause expects have made some error, or will you be paying in cash?"
msgstr "Huh, Mr. Ripley, I cannot find any money in your account. Could pause expects have made some error, or will you be paying in cash?"

#: 04_11P02
msgctxt "04_11P02"
msgid "Of course, of course."
msgstr "Of course, of course."

#: 04_12N01
msgctxt "04_12N01"
msgid "Mr. Ripley, as I said, my records show no money in your account. Would you prefer to pay in cash?"
msgstr "Mr. Ripley, as I said, my records show no money in your account. Would you prefer to pay in cash?"

#: 04_15N01
msgctxt "04_15N01"
msgid "Goodbye!"
msgstr "Goodbye!"

#: 04_15P01
msgctxt "04_15P01"
msgid "Better make it cash."
msgstr "Better make it cash."

#: 04_16N01
msgctxt "04_16N01"
msgid "Goodbye!"
msgstr "Goodbye!"

#: 04_16P01
msgctxt "04_16P01"
msgid "I'm ready to leave now, Qian Shu."
msgstr "I'm ready to leave now, Qian Shu."

#: 04_17N01
msgctxt "04_17N01"
msgid "Very good, Mr. Ripley."
msgstr "Very good, Mr. Ripley."

#: 04_17P01
msgctxt "04_17P01"
msgid "Change my mind!"
msgstr "Change my mind!"

#: 0507P02A
msgctxt "0507P02A"
msgid "Twelve Trees and I go way back."
msgstr "Twelve Trees and I go way back."

#: 05_01N01
msgctxt "05_01N01"
msgid "Certainly sir, we welcome scholars from many lands to the Hall of Classics. Are you a scholar?"
msgstr "Certainly sir, we welcome scholars from many lands to the Hall of Classics. Are you a scholar?"

#: 05_01P01
msgctxt "05_01P01"
msgid "Do you speak English?"
msgstr "Do you speak English?"

#: 05_02N01
msgctxt "05_02N01"
msgid "The first emperor sent Mastelou across the world to search for the elixir of life."
msgstr "The first emperor sent Mastelou across the world to search for the elixir of life."

#: 05_02N02
msgctxt "05_02N02"
msgid "The stone tablet of the Master Lu."
msgstr "The stone tablet of the Master Lu."

#: 05_02N03
msgctxt "05_02N03"
msgid "These tablets contain the enduring record of all Chinese knowledge."
msgstr "These tablets contain the enduring record of all Chinese knowledge."

#: 05_02N04
msgctxt "05_02N04"
msgid "No, those passes are obtained in the Official Records Building."
msgstr "No, those passes are obtained in the Official Records Building."

#: 05_02P01
msgctxt "05_02P01"
msgid "I'm interested in learning all I can of Master Lu."
msgstr "I'm interested in learning all I can of Master Lu."

#: 05_02P02
msgctxt "05_02P02"
msgid "What's in that building behind you?"
msgstr "What's in that building behind you?"

#: 05_02P03
msgctxt "05_02P03"
msgid "Can you tell me about these tablets?"
msgstr "Can you tell me about these tablets?"

#: 05_02P04
msgctxt "05_02P04"
msgid "You don't happen to have a pass that would get me by that official at the far end of the street, do you?"
msgstr "You don't happen to have a pass that would get me by that official at the far end of the street, do you?"

#: 05_03N01
msgctxt "05_03N01"
msgid "A complex field of study."
msgstr "A complex field of study."

#: 05_03N02
msgctxt "05_03N02"
msgid "For what purpose?"
msgstr "For what purpose?"

#: 05_03P01
msgctxt "05_03P01"
msgid "I guess you could say I'm a student of life."
msgstr "I guess you could say I'm a student of life."

#: 05_03P02
msgctxt "05_03P02"
msgid "I collect oddities, curiosities of history and nature."
msgstr "I collect oddities, curiosities of history and nature."

#: 05_04N01
msgctxt "05_04N01"
msgid "One... I know of no others..."
msgstr "One... I know of no others..."

#: 05_04N02
msgctxt "05_04N02"
msgid "Indeed. How may I assist you in your study of life?"
msgstr "Indeed. How may I assist you in your study of life?"

#: 05_04P01
msgctxt "05_04P01"
msgid "Oh, neither. It is one of the great libraries of the world."
msgstr "Oh, neither. It is one of the great libraries of the world."

#: 05_04P02
msgctxt "05_04P02"
msgid "Too big to be either one."
msgstr "Too big to be either one."

#: 05_05N01
msgctxt "05_05N01"
msgid "Then perhaps you should study life at one of those."
msgstr "Then perhaps you should study life at one of those."

#: 05_05N02
msgctxt "05_05N02"
msgid "Indeed. How may I assist you in your study of life?"
msgstr "Indeed. How may I assist you in your study of life?"

#: 05_05P01
msgctxt "05_05P01"
msgid "Well, there is the British Museum, the Library of Congress..."
msgstr "Well, there is the British Museum, the Library of Congress..."

#: 05_05P02
msgctxt "05_05P02"
msgid "None of that can come close to the magnificence of this place."
msgstr "None of that can come close to the magnificence of this place."

#: 05_06N01
msgctxt "05_06N01"
msgid "Oh?"
msgstr "Oh?"

#: 05_06P01
msgctxt "05_06P01"
msgid "Say, I guess we got off on the wrong foot before."
msgstr "Say, I guess we got off on the wrong foot before."

#: 05_07N01
msgctxt "05_07N01"
msgid "You may have been lucky."
msgstr "You may have been lucky."

#: 05_07N02
msgctxt "05_07N02"
msgid "At that time, Master Lu's tablet was openly displayed. However, the very night this 12 trees examined it, an attempt was made to steal the tablet."
msgstr "At that time, Master Lu's tablet was openly displayed. However, the very night this 12 trees examined it, an attempt was made to steal the tablet."

#: 05_07P01
msgctxt "05_07P01"
msgid "No, I just missed him in Thebes."
msgstr "No, I just missed him in Thebes."

#: 05_07P02
msgctxt "05_07P02"
msgid "Oh, yeah!"
msgstr "Oh, yeah!"

#: 05_08N01
msgctxt "05_08N01"
msgid "The tomb of the first emperor, built by Master Lu, lies in the Xian province. Master Lu is also with his ancestors."
msgstr "The tomb of the first emperor, built by Master Lu, lies in the Xian province. Master Lu is also with his ancestors."

#: 05_08N02
msgctxt "05_08N02"
msgid "He studied many languages and system of writing. On his return, he created a stone tablet with hieroglyphics or ideograms in three different scripts."
msgstr "He studied many languages and system of writing. On his return, he created a stone tablet with hieroglyphics or ideograms in three different scripts."

#: 05_08N03
msgctxt "05_08N03"
msgid "It is said he visited Sikkim and an island in the Pacific with great stone heads."
msgstr "It is said he visited Sikkim and an island in the Pacific with great stone heads."

#: 05_08N99
msgctxt "05_08N99"
msgid "He studied many languages and systems of writing. On his return, he created a stone tablet with hieroglyphics or ideograms in three different scripts."
msgstr "He studied many languages and systems of writing. On his return, he created a stone tablet with hieroglyphics or ideograms in three different scripts."

#: 05_08P01
msgctxt "05_08P01"
msgid "Did he find the elixir of life?"
msgstr "Did he find the elixir of life?"

#: 05_08P02
msgctxt "05_08P02"
msgid "What did Master Lu learn in his travels?"
msgstr "What did Master Lu learn in his travels?"

#: 05_08P03
msgctxt "05_08P03"
msgid "Where did Master Lu go?"
msgstr "Where did Master Lu go?"

#: 05_09N01
msgctxt "05_09N01"
msgid "We would be very interested in such a key."
msgstr "We would be very interested in such a key."

#: 05_09P01
msgctxt "05_09P01"
msgid "I may know where to find a key to deciphering that tablet."
msgstr "I may know where to find a key to deciphering that tablet."

#: 05_09P02
msgctxt "05_09P02"
msgid "If someone were to find the key to that tablet..."
msgstr "If someone were to find the key to that tablet..."

#: 05_10N01
msgctxt "05_10N01"
msgid "I am afraid not. Several weeks ago, an archaeologist named 12 Trees asked to see the tablet."
msgstr "I am afraid not. Several weeks ago, an archaeologist named 12 Trees asked to see the tablet."

#: 05_10P01
msgctxt "05_10P01"
msgid "May I see it?"
msgstr "May I see it?"

#: 05_11N01
msgctxt "05_11N01"
msgid "A foreigner? I doubt if any foreigner could hope to be an expert on Master Lu."
msgstr "A foreigner? I doubt if any foreigner could hope to be an expert on Master Lu."

#: 05_11P01
msgctxt "05_11P01"
msgid "Twelve trees. That's the name the baron mentioned. Chap's supposed to be somewhat of an expert on Master Lu."
msgstr "Twelve trees. That's the name the baron mentioned. Chap's supposed to be somewhat of an expert on Master Lu."

#: 05_12N01
msgctxt "05_12N01"
msgid "Uh, no, I did not. You do not know this 12 Trees, then?"
msgstr "Uh, no, I did not. You do not know this 12 Trees, then?"

#: 05_12P01
msgctxt "05_12P01"
msgid "Did you speak with him?"
msgstr "Did you speak with him?"

#: 05_13N01
msgctxt "05_13N01"
msgid "Ah, I see you are a scholar. That is true. It is my belief that he was blinded by the ancients to preserve our true heritage."
msgstr "Ah, I see you are a scholar. That is true. It is my belief that he was blinded by the ancients to preserve our true heritage."

#: 05_13P01
msgctxt "05_13P01"
msgid "It's surprising Qin Shi Huangdi overlooked him when he tried to destroy all record of China's past."
msgstr "It's surprising Qin Shi Huangdi overlooked him when he tried to destroy all record of China's past."

#: 05_14N01
msgctxt "05_14N01"
msgid "Beyond the Archway, the Official Guards."
msgstr "Beyond the Archway, the Official Guards."

#: 05_14P01
msgctxt "05_14P01"
msgid "And where is that?"
msgstr "And where is that?"

#: 05_15N01
msgctxt "05_15N01"
msgid "Also, an ancient city high in the mountains of South America we now call the Andes."
msgstr "Also, an ancient city high in the mountains of South America we now call the Andes."

#: 05_15P01
msgctxt "05_15P01"
msgid "Somehow I knew you were going to say that."
msgstr "Somehow I knew you were going to say that."

#: 05_16N01
msgctxt "05_16N01"
msgid "And which is the Hall of Classics? A nook or a cranny?"
msgstr "And which is the Hall of Classics? A nook or a cranny?"

#: 05_16P01
msgctxt "05_16P01"
msgid "You can say that again. You wouldn't believe some of the nooks and crannies of this world I find myself rooting about in."
msgstr "You can say that again. You wouldn't believe some of the nooks and crannies of this world I find myself rooting about in."

#: 05_17N01
msgctxt "05_17N01"
msgid "For profit."
msgstr "For profit."

#: 05_17P01
msgctxt "05_17P01"
msgid "Well, to share with other people."
msgstr "Well, to share with other people."

#: 05_18N01
msgctxt "05_18N01"
msgid "I am afraid the Hall of Classics serves knowledge, not avarice."
msgstr "I am afraid the Hall of Classics serves knowledge, not avarice."

#: 05_18P01
msgctxt "05_18P01"
msgid "Not so far, but that's the general idea."
msgstr "Not so far, but that's the general idea."

#: 05_19N01
msgctxt "05_19N01"
msgid "It is a wise man who admits he is wrong. Wise men are welcomed here."
msgstr "It is a wise man who admits he is wrong. Wise men are welcomed here."

#: 05_19P01
msgctxt "05_19P01"
msgid "I'd like to apologize."
msgstr "I'd like to apologize."

#: 05_20N01
msgctxt "05_20N01"
msgid "At that time Master Lu's tablet was openly displayed. However, the very night this twelve trees examined it, an attempt was made to steal the tablet."
msgstr "At that time Master Lu's tablet was openly displayed. However, the very night this twelve trees examined it, an attempt was made to steal the tablet."

#: 05_20P01
msgctxt "05_20P01"
msgid "Why do you say that?"
msgstr "Why do you say that?"

#: 05_21N01
msgctxt "05_21N01"
msgid "Nevertheless, these are difficult times, and no one may see the tablet."
msgstr "Nevertheless, these are difficult times, and no one may see the tablet."

#: 05_21P01
msgctxt "05_21P01"
msgid "You have no proof he was behind the theft."
msgstr "You have no proof he was behind the theft."

#: 05_23P01
msgctxt "05_23P01"
msgid "Ah, guess not."
msgstr "Ah, guess not."

#: 05_24N01
msgctxt "05_24N01"
msgid "The tablet is believed to hold the secret of the First Emperor's tomb. It is, as you may know, protected by deadly traps created by Master Lu. That is why, even after all these centuries, the tomb has never been opened. Unfortunately, none have been able to decipher the tablet."
msgstr "The tablet is believed to hold the secret of the First Emperor's tomb. It is, as you may know, protected by deadly traps created by Master Lu. That is why, even after all these centuries, the tomb has never been opened. Unfortunately, none have been able to decipher the tablet."

#: 05_24P01
msgctxt "05_24P01"
msgid "Do you know what they mean?"
msgstr "Do you know what they mean?"

#: 05_25N01
msgctxt "05_25N01"
msgid "The Emperor's seal is a talisman of great power. Master Lu felt that the world of his day was too troubled to use such power wisely. It was his hope that one day all peoples would be united in peace and harmony. The shared knowledge of such a global union would be the key to unlocking the tomb."
msgstr "The Emperor's seal is a talisman of great power. Master Lu felt that the world of his day was too troubled to use such power wisely. It was his hope that one day all peoples would be united in peace and harmony. The shared knowledge of such a global union would be the key to unlocking the tomb."

#: 05_25P01
msgctxt "05_25P01"
msgid "Why would Lou have made it so difficult? Was there no one he trusted?"
msgstr "Why would Lou have made it so difficult? Was there no one he trusted?"

#: 05_26N01
msgctxt "05_26N01"
msgid "Also, an ancient city high in the mountains of South America we now call the Andes."
msgstr "Also, an ancient city high in the mountains of South America we now call the Andes."

#: 05_26P01
msgctxt "05_26P01"
msgid "Easter Island!"
msgstr "Easter Island!"

#: 05_27N01
msgctxt "05_27N01"
msgid "Indeed. Lou's tablet holds scripts from each of these ancient lands."
msgstr "Indeed. Lou's tablet holds scripts from each of these ancient lands."

#: 05_27P01
msgctxt "05_27P01"
msgid "With any luck, I can reach that through Lima as well."
msgstr "With any luck, I can reach that through Lima as well."

#: 05_28N01
msgctxt "05_28N01"
msgid "What men?"
msgstr "What men?"

#: 05_28P01
msgctxt "05_28P01"
msgid "There have been attempts to find out what I know by men who would not hesitate to kill."
msgstr "There have been attempts to find out what I know by men who would not hesitate to kill."

#: 05_29N01
msgctxt "05_29N01"
msgid "Mr. Ripley, you realize what these men may be after."
msgstr "Mr. Ripley, you realize what these men may be after."

#: 05_29P01
msgctxt "05_29P01"
msgid "Maybe the same men who tried to steal the tablet."
msgstr "Maybe the same men who tried to steal the tablet."

#: 05_30P01
msgctxt "05_30P01"
msgid "I intend to find out."
msgstr "I intend to find out."

#: 05_31N01
msgctxt "05_31N01"
msgid "The man who holds that seal, holds Taina in the palm of his hand."
msgstr "The man who holds that seal, holds Taina in the palm of his hand."

#: 05_31P01
msgctxt "05_31P01"
msgid "The Emperor's Seal."
msgstr "The Emperor's Seal."

#: 05_32N01
msgctxt "05_32N01"
msgid "What do you propose?"
msgstr "What do you propose?"

#: 05_32P01
msgctxt "05_32P01"
msgid "Maybe all of the Far East. That's why it's so important the wrong man never gains the seal."
msgstr "Maybe all of the Far East. That's why it's so important the wrong man never gains the seal."

#: 05_33N01
msgctxt "05_33N01"
msgid "To what end?"
msgstr "To what end?"

#: 05_33P01
msgctxt "05_33P01"
msgid "If I locate the key, may I see the tablet?"
msgstr "If I locate the key, may I see the tablet?"

#: 05_34N01
msgctxt "05_34N01"
msgid "But how do I know you would not try to use the power of the seal?"
msgstr "But how do I know you would not try to use the power of the seal?"

#: 05_34P01
msgctxt "05_34P01"
msgid "To enter the tomb of the First Emperor, recover the seal, and bring it here to you for safekeeping."
msgstr "To enter the tomb of the First Emperor, recover the seal, and bring it here to you for safekeeping."

#: 05_35N01
msgctxt "05_35N01"
msgid "If you bring the key, then we will talk."
msgstr "If you bring the key, then we will talk."

#: 05_35P01
msgctxt "05_35P01"
msgid "You have only my word. But who else have you got?"
msgstr "You have only my word. But who else have you got?"

#: 05_36P01
msgctxt "05_36P01"
msgid "I've wheeled and dealed a good bit of my day, and you, sir, are one sharp customer."
msgstr "I've wheeled and dealed a good bit of my day, and you, sir, are one sharp customer."

#: 05_37N01
msgctxt "05_37N01"
msgid "Also an ancient city, high in mountains of South America, we now call the Andes."
msgstr "Also an ancient city, high in mountains of South America, we now call the Andes."

#: 05_37P01
msgctxt "05_37P01"
msgid "I expect I'll have to go through Lima, Peru to get there."
msgstr "I expect I'll have to go through Lima, Peru to get there."

#: 05_38N01
msgctxt "05_38N01"
msgid "Indeed, loose tablet holds grip from each of these ancient lands."
msgstr "Indeed, loose tablet holds grip from each of these ancient lands."

#: 05_38P01
msgctxt "05_38P01"
