msgid "Ah, from Mei's aunt and uncle in London. Understand Mei Chen's concern for mother would be happy to assist in any way we can. It just might work."
msgstr "Ah, from Mei's aunt and uncle in London. Understand Mei Chen's concern for mother would be happy to assist in any way we can. It just might work."

