msgctxt "203R02"
msgid "You may be right. Luckily, when he ordered the past erased, he neglected the stone tablets in the Hall of Classics."
msgstr "You may be right. Luckily, when he ordered the past erased, he neglected the stone tablets in the Hall of Classics."

