msgctxt "203R03"
msgid "Severed heads? What crime introduced those gentlemen to the executioner's axe?"
msgstr "Severed heads? What crime introduced those gentlemen to the executioner's axe?"

#: 203R04
msgctxt "203R04"
msgid "You attend to it, Mei. But I wager I'll be greeting you from the inside when you return."
msgstr "You attend to it, Mei. But I wager I'll be greeting you from the inside when you return."

#: 203R05
msgctxt "203R05"
msgid "Don't worry, Mei. I won't stick my neck out."
msgstr "Don't worry, Mei. I won't stick my neck out."

