msgctxt "203R09"
msgid "She's holding her bird seed in a soldier's helmet from the Great War. I wonder how she comes to have it. I'll wager there's a story there."
msgstr "She's holding her bird seed in a soldier's helmet from the Great War. I wonder how she comes to have it. I'll wager there's a story there."

