msgctxt "203R64"
msgid "Just giving him the helmet won't get him out of my hair. He'll probably just want more. I wonder if there's some other way I can use it to distract him."
msgstr "Just giving him the helmet won't get him out of my hair. He'll probably just want more. I wonder if there's some other way I can use it to distract him."

