msgstr "I think I'll leave it to the police of this fine city to keep the baskets applied."

#: 20437P01
msgctxt "20437P01"
msgid "I expect I'll have to go through Lima, Peru to get there."
msgstr "I expect I'll have to go through Lima, Peru to get there."

#: 20438P01
msgctxt "20438P01"
msgid "But this is fantastic! To think a Chinese sage may have visited the Americas hundreds of years before Columbus, or even Magellan's circumnavigation of the globe!"
msgstr "But this is fantastic! To think a Chinese sage may have visited the Americas hundreds of years before Columbus, or even Magellan's circumnavigation of the globe!"

#: 204M01
