msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "Yes?"

#: 204M02A
msgctxt "204M02A"
msgid "Whoops!"
msgstr "Whoops!"

#: 204M02B
msgctxt "204M02B"
msgid "Robert, you could have been more diplomatic."
msgstr "Robert, you could have been more diplomatic."

#: 204M03
msgctxt "204M03"
msgid "But Robert, what if he is the one who tried to kill you and Feng Li?"
msgstr "But Robert, what if he is the one who tried to kill you and Feng Li?"

#: 204M04
msgctxt "204M04"
msgid "These are Lao Tzu's famous writings on peace. To find peace, he says, one must manifest plainness, embrace simplicity, reduce selfishness, have few desires."
msgstr "These are Lao Tzu's famous writings on peace. To find peace, he says, one must manifest plainness, embrace simplicity, reduce selfishness, have few desires."

#: 204M05
msgctxt "204M05"
msgid "These are early Chinese writings. These inscriptions were originally carved on bones and tortoise shells and were used for divinations performed for the kings of the Shang dynasty."
msgstr "These are early Chinese writings. These inscriptions were originally carved on bones and tortoise shells and were used for divinations performed for the kings of the Shang dynasty."

#: 204M06
msgctxt "204M06"
msgid "The Analects of Confucius. My grandmother used to read from them when I was a young girl."
msgstr "The Analects of Confucius. My grandmother used to read from them when I was a young girl."

#: 204M07
msgctxt "204M07"
msgid "Hmm, these are excerpts from the Shi Qing, ancient Chinese poems that date back to the 10th century B.C."
msgstr "Hmm, these are excerpts from the Shi Qing, ancient Chinese poems that date back to the 10th century B.C."

#: 204M08
msgctxt "204M08"
msgid "Ah, Li Sao. In English it is called Encountering Sorrow. A poetic story of a soul in torment, because it cannot find what it is looking for. I know this poem well."
msgstr "Ah, Li Sao. In English it is called Encountering Sorrow. A poetic story of a soul in torment, because it cannot find what it is looking for. I know this poem well."

#: 204M09
msgctxt "204M09"
msgid "The Shuxi tells of China's history up to the Han dynasty. Of course, this is just a portion of it."
msgstr "The Shuxi tells of China's history up to the Han dynasty. Of course, this is just a portion of it."

#: 204M10
msgctxt "204M10"
msgid "These tell some of the earliest stories of Chinese history."
msgstr "These tell some of the earliest stories of Chinese history."

#: 204M11
msgctxt "204M11"
msgid "These are more writings by Lao Tzu."
msgstr "These are more writings by Lao Tzu."

#: 204M12
msgctxt "204M12"
msgid "These are more poems from the Xiu Qing."
msgstr "These are more poems from the Xiu Qing."

#: 204M13
msgctxt "204M13"
msgid "More from the Analects of Confucius."
msgstr "More from the Analects of Confucius."

#: 204M14
msgctxt "204M14"
msgid "These are more of the Tao Te Ching."
msgstr "These are more of the Tao Te Ching."

#: 204M15
msgctxt "204M15"
msgid "These are more of Xiu Qing - 'The records of the historian'."
msgstr "These are more of Xiu Qing - 'The records of the historian'."

#: 204M16
msgctxt "204M16"
msgid "Don't worry."
msgstr "Don't worry."

#: 204M17
msgctxt "204M17"
msgid "I expect to hear very soon."
msgstr "I expect to hear very soon."

#: 204M18
msgctxt "204M18"
msgid "I'm doing everything I can."
msgstr "I'm doing everything I can."

#: 204M20
msgctxt "204M20"
msgid "No. The Japanese control all of the Northeast now. They are holding up all papers. It is very difficult."
msgstr "No. The Japanese control all of the Northeast now. They are holding up all papers. It is very difficult."

#: 204M21
msgctxt "204M21"
msgid "I think it comforts her that I am here, but she is very afraid. The Japanese soldiers swagger in the streets as if they already own China. If war comes, she will have nowhere to go."
msgstr "I think it comforts her that I am here, but she is very afraid. The Japanese soldiers swagger in the streets as if they already own China. If war comes, she will have nowhere to go."

#: 204M22
msgctxt "204M22"
msgid "If these ancient languages survived, a translation of the tablet would have been made long ago."
msgstr "If these ancient languages survived, a translation of the tablet would have been made long ago."

#: 204M23
msgctxt "204M23"
msgid "If Baron von Saltsam has a key to the tablet, you might not have to go to all those places."
msgstr "If Baron von Saltsam has a key to the tablet, you might not have to go to all those places."

#: 204M24
msgctxt "204M24"
msgid "I don't know. It all sounds so impossible."
msgstr "I don't know. It all sounds so impossible."

