msgid "Ah, Mei, what kept you?"
msgstr "Ah, Mei, what kept you?"

#: 204R02
msgctxt "204R02"
msgid "It took some doing, I confess. I gather you've obtained the necessary pass."
msgstr "It took some doing, I confess. I gather you've obtained the necessary pass."

#: 204R03
msgctxt "204R03"
msgid "Splendid! Returning will be much easier."
msgstr "Splendid! Returning will be much easier."

#: 204R03A
msgctxt "204R03A"
msgid "Looks like Confucian priests aren't much concerned with capitalism."
msgstr "Looks like Confucian priests aren't much concerned with capitalism."

#: 204R03B
msgctxt "204R03B"
msgid "Next time I will be."
msgstr "Next time I will be."

#: 204R03C
msgctxt "204R03C"
msgid "We have a deal."
msgstr "We have a deal."

#: 204R04
msgctxt "204R04"
msgid "Then I'll have to tread very carefully, won't I? Didn't I tell you Peiping in the spring would be interesting, Mei?"
msgstr "Then I'll have to tread very carefully, won't I? Didn't I tell you Peiping in the spring would be interesting, Mei?"

#: 204R06
msgctxt "204R06"
msgid "The Hall of Classics is immense, yet it is only a small part of the Imperial School."
msgstr "The Hall of Classics is immense, yet it is only a small part of the Imperial School."

#: 204R07
msgctxt "204R07"
msgid "An exquisite bronze lantern, obviously used to light the walkway at night."
msgstr "An exquisite bronze lantern, obviously used to light the walkway at night."

#: 204R08
msgctxt "204R08"
msgid "Whatever is in there has been afforded a place of great honor."
msgstr "Whatever is in there has been afforded a place of great honor."

#: 204R09
