msgctxt "21_06N02"
msgid "It is written, only he who has studied longest knows the hidden way."
msgstr "It is written, only he who has studied longest knows the hidden way."

#: 21_06P01
msgctxt "21_06P01"
msgid "How do I find the path to enlightenment?"
msgstr "How do I find the path to enlightenment?"

