msgctxt "21_06P02"
msgid "Has anyone found the path to enlightenment?"
msgstr "Has anyone found the path to enlightenment?"

#: 21_07N01
msgctxt "21_07N01"
msgid "To those who ask the question, I am instructed to say only this. None of my brothers will find what he seeks until he has the correct prayer wheel."
msgstr "To those who ask the question, I am instructed to say only this. None of my brothers will find what he seeks until he has the correct prayer wheel."

