#: 305R01
msgctxt "305R01"
msgid "Mrs. B. McDonald of Washington, Kansas owned a parrot called Billy. After 31 years, Billy laid an egg. Now she calls him Nellie."
msgstr "Mrs. B. McDonald of Washington, Kansas owned a parrot called Billy. After 31 years, Billy laid an egg. Now she calls him Nellie."

#: 305R02
msgctxt "305R02"
msgid "The smallest postcard ever mailed. A message of 40 words written on the back of a stamp was delivered promptly."
msgstr "The smallest postcard ever mailed. A message of 40 words written on the back of a stamp was delivered promptly."

#: 305R03
msgctxt "305R03"
msgid "A tree growing out of a chimney in Aberdeley, Wales."
msgstr "A tree growing out of a chimney in Aberdeley, Wales."

#: 305R04
msgctxt "305R04"
msgid "A lemon 22 inches around and weighing 4 pounds."
msgstr "A lemon 22 inches around and weighing 4 pounds."

