msgctxt "305R05"
msgid "This restaurant in Yuma, Arizona posted a sign reading, free meals every day, the sun doesn't shine. For 16 years they never had to serve a free meal."
msgstr "This restaurant in Yuma, Arizona posted a sign reading, free meals every day, the sun doesn't shine. For 16 years they never had to serve a free meal."

#: 305R06
msgctxt "305R06"
