msgctxt "305R07"
msgid "A truck in Indianapolis bearing the sign, a blind man is driving this truck, is actually owned by a dealer in window blinds."
msgstr "A truck in Indianapolis bearing the sign, a blind man is driving this truck, is actually owned by a dealer in window blinds."

