msgstr "A hollow log in Porterville, California is used as a garage for automobiles."

#: 305R10
msgctxt "305R10"
msgid "Burnt toast artfully fashioned into a likeness of the Mona Lisa. This is new. The customers will eat it up."
msgstr "Burnt toast artfully fashioned into a likeness of the Mona Lisa. This is new. The customers will eat it up."

#: 305R11
msgctxt "305R11"
msgid "Ah, the Mona Lisa made from burnt toast Feng Li mentioned. Exquisite!"
msgstr "Ah, the Mona Lisa made from burnt toast Feng Li mentioned. Exquisite!"

#: 305R12
msgctxt "305R12"
msgid "This hammerhead shark fell out of the sky during a storm near Emporia, Kansas, over 600 miles from the nearest ocean."
msgstr "This hammerhead shark fell out of the sky during a storm near Emporia, Kansas, over 600 miles from the nearest ocean."

#: 305R13
msgctxt "305R13"
msgid "This hourglass, the world's largest, is filled with gigantic jelly beans and keeps perfect time."
msgstr "This hourglass, the world's largest, is filled with gigantic jelly beans and keeps perfect time."

#: 305R14
msgctxt "305R14"
msgid "Bachelor Enoch Sharp of Pell, Kentucky, fashioned this button suit and hat from nearly seven thousand buttons."
msgstr "Bachelor Enoch Sharp of Pell, Kentucky, fashioned this button suit and hat from nearly seven thousand buttons."

#: 305R15
msgctxt "305R15"
msgid "The sign reads, new exhibits coming soon. Why, I hope that's true. With any luck, I'll be able to find some more in my travels."
msgstr "The sign reads, new exhibits coming soon. Why, I hope that's true. With any luck, I'll be able to find some more in my travels."

#: 305R16
msgctxt "305R16"
msgid "Feng Li's pet turtle. He loves the little fella. Changes the candle on its back as often as he changes his own."
msgstr "Feng Li's pet turtle. He loves the little fella. Changes the candle on its back as often as he changes his own."

#: 305R16A
msgctxt "305R16A"
msgid "Feng Li's pet turtle lives there. When I'm done with him, I'd better see to it he gets back safely."
msgstr "Feng Li's pet turtle lives there. When I'm done with him, I'd better see to it he gets back safely."

#: 305R16B
msgctxt "305R16B"
msgid "Fang Li's pet turtle."
msgstr "Fang Li's pet turtle."

