msgctxt "305R19"
msgid "I better take good care of a little critter. Feng Li thinks the world of him."
msgstr "I better take good care of a little critter. Feng Li thinks the world of him."

#: 305R19B
msgctxt "305R19B"
msgid "Feng Li would be crushed if I gave away his little friend."
msgstr "Feng Li would be crushed if I gave away his little friend."

