msgctxt "305R20"
msgid "Feng Li's turtle loves these things. Actually, so does Feng Li."
msgstr "Feng Li's turtle loves these things. Actually, so does Feng Li."

#: 305R21
msgctxt "305R21"
msgid "These gigantic statues stand sentinel on lonely Easter Island in the South Pacific. Built by a forgotten race, their meaning has never been ascertained."
msgstr "These gigantic statues stand sentinel on lonely Easter Island in the South Pacific. Built by a forgotten race, their meaning has never been ascertained."

#: 305R22
msgctxt "305R22"
msgid "The land of China was named after Qin Shi Huangdi, her first emperor. He built the Great Wall in China."
msgstr "The land of China was named after Qin Shi Huangdi, her first emperor. He built the Great Wall in China."

#: 305R23
msgctxt "305R23"
msgid "Qin Shi Huang, first emperor of China, destroyed all literature and executed every historian in order that history would begin with him."
msgstr "Qin Shi Huang, first emperor of China, destroyed all literature and executed every historian in order that history would begin with him."

#: 305R23A
msgctxt "305R23A"
msgid "However, he overlooked these stone tablets in Peiping, on which Chinese history was engraved."
msgstr "However, he overlooked these stone tablets in Peiping, on which Chinese history was engraved."

#: 305R24
msgctxt "305R24"
msgid "I am fascinated by the epitaphs found on tombstones all over the world."
msgstr "I am fascinated by the epitaphs found on tombstones all over the world."

#: 305R25
msgctxt "305R25"
msgid "This collection of epitaphs is from the graveyard where Baron von Seltsam was laid to rest."
msgstr "This collection of epitaphs is from the graveyard where Baron von Seltsam was laid to rest."

#: 305R26
msgctxt "305R26"
msgid "The castle built to honor the Ace of Spades, erected by Otto, 6th Baron von Seltsam, in the shape of the playing card that won him the fortunate cost."
msgstr "The castle built to honor the Ace of Spades, erected by Otto, 6th Baron von Seltsam, in the shape of the playing card that won him the fortunate cost."

#: 305R27
msgctxt "305R27"
msgid "The lost city of Mokomoche, high in the Andes Mountains."
msgstr "The lost city of Mokomoche, high in the Andes Mountains."

#: 305R28
msgctxt "305R28"
msgid "The holy men of the unique temple of the hidden way dedicate their lives to unraveling the puzzles of the human condition. Even to join the temple, one must pass several mind-boggling tests."
msgstr "The holy men of the unique temple of the hidden way dedicate their lives to unraveling the puzzles of the human condition. Even to join the temple, one must pass several mind-boggling tests."

#: 305R29
msgctxt "305R29"
msgid "The curse of the Romanov Emerald. Tsar Peter III was deposed and slain. His son Paul wore the emerald once and was assassinated."
msgstr "The curse of the Romanov Emerald. Tsar Peter III was deposed and slain. His son Paul wore the emerald once and was assassinated."

#: 305R29A
msgctxt "305R29A"
msgid "Alexander II discovered the Emerald 80 years later and was blown up by a bomb. His grandson Nicholas II was executed by the Bolsheviks."
msgstr "Alexander II discovered the Emerald 80 years later and was blown up by a bomb. His grandson Nicholas II was executed by the Bolsheviks."

#: 305R29B
msgctxt "305R29B"
msgid "It now lies at the bottom of a gorge in Peru. I can only hope it does not bring ruin to the rulers of that beautiful South American country."
msgstr "It now lies at the bottom of a gorge in Peru. I can only hope it does not bring ruin to the rulers of that beautiful South American country."

#: 305R30
msgctxt "305R30"
msgid "This room contains cartoons featured in newspapers all over the world."
msgstr "This room contains cartoons featured in newspapers all over the world."

#: 305R31
msgctxt "305R31"
msgid "Da Vinci's famous painting rendered in toast. It's an honor to bring great art like this to the public."
msgstr "Da Vinci's famous painting rendered in toast. It's an honor to bring great art like this to the public."

#: 305R32
