msgstr "A Chinese rebus amulet. Two musical stones joined by a disc. It's inscribed, may you be assured, double good fortune."

#: 305R40
msgctxt "305R40"
msgid "I better not let him know I borrowed his turtle. He might not understand."
msgstr "I better not let him know I borrowed his turtle. He might not understand."

#: 305R41
msgctxt "305R41"
msgid "That shrunken head from Peru is not of any great antiquity, and seems to have been stitched together in some haste."
msgstr "That shrunken head from Peru is not of any great antiquity, and seems to have been stitched together in some haste."

#: 305R42
msgctxt "305R42"
msgid "A pre-Columbian wheeled toy from the Andes Mountains. The Inca never discovered any practical application for the wheel, yet on the very spot where centuries later their civilization would flourish, the wheel was used as locomotion for a toy duck. Astounding!"
msgstr "A pre-Columbian wheeled toy from the Andes Mountains. The Inca never discovered any practical application for the wheel, yet on the very spot where centuries later their civilization would flourish, the wheel was used as locomotion for a toy duck. Astounding!"

