#: 407R15
msgctxt "407R15"
msgid "A thick glass bottle with many curious features. It's girded with an iron support of some kind. There are three small holes set in its sides. The largest opening is at the top. About the only thing unremarkable about it is the familiar shape."
msgstr "A thick glass bottle with many curious features. It's girded with an iron support of some kind. There are three small holes set in its sides. The largest opening is at the top. About the only thing unremarkable about it is the familiar shape."

#: 407R15A
