msgid "A thick glass bottle with many curious features."
msgstr "A thick glass bottle with many curious features."

#: 407R16
msgctxt "407R16"
msgid "Say, what's that at the bottom of the glass?"
msgstr "Say, what's that at the bottom of the glass?"

#: 407R16A
msgctxt "407R16A"
msgid "The Romanov Emerald sits at the bottom."
msgstr "The Romanov Emerald sits at the bottom."

#: 407R17
msgctxt "407R17"
msgid "A huge emerald set in a brooch. The brooch pin is stuck in a cork."
msgstr "A huge emerald set in a brooch. The brooch pin is stuck in a cork."

#: 407R17A
msgctxt "407R17A"
msgid "The accursed Romanov Emerald. I found it!"
msgstr "The accursed Romanov Emerald. I found it!"

