msgstr "The bottle's iron support is being attached to the gear wheel."

#: 407R22
msgctxt "407R22"
msgid "The periodic table. I had to memorize every last one of the elements when I was a boy. It's the kind of useless knowledge schools insist on cramming into your brain."
msgstr "The periodic table. I had to memorize every last one of the elements when I was a boy. It's the kind of useless knowledge schools insist on cramming into your brain."

#: 407R23
msgctxt "407R23"
msgid "An armored steel cabinet with no sign of a keyhole, or any mechanism for opening it. A metal rod runs from a piston in the ceiling through the top of the cabinet."
msgstr "An armored steel cabinet with no sign of a keyhole, or any mechanism for opening it. A metal rod runs from a piston in the ceiling through the top of the cabinet."

