msgstr "The sixth in a row of seven soldiers wearing purple skirts."

#: 814R12
msgctxt "814R12"
msgid "The seventh in a row of seven soldiers wearing purple skirts."
msgstr "The seventh in a row of seven soldiers wearing purple skirts."

