msgctxt "814R15"
msgid "The weight of Mount Li has taken a toll on the ceiling of this corridor."
msgstr "The weight of Mount Li has taken a toll on the ceiling of this corridor."

#: 814R18
msgctxt "814R18"
msgid "One of the terracotta horses in this corridor has fallen on its side."
msgstr "One of the terracotta horses in this corridor has fallen on its side."

#: 814R21
msgctxt "814R21"
msgid "It's too heavy to lift, but I might be able to push it."
msgstr "It's too heavy to lift, but I might be able to push it."

#: 814R26
msgctxt "814R26"
msgid "The chariot won't budge an inch."
msgstr "The chariot won't budge an inch."

#: 824R02
msgctxt "824R02"
msgid "The first in a row of seven soldiers wearing yellow skirts."
msgstr "The first in a row of seven soldiers wearing yellow skirts."

#: 824R03
