msgstr "Robert!"

#: 852R01
msgctxt "852R01"
msgid "The dirt wall was very thin here between the root cellar and some sort of large cave. May, come look at this!"
msgstr "The dirt wall was very thin here between the root cellar and some sort of large cave. May, come look at this!"

#: 852R02
msgctxt "852R02"
