msgctxt "860R01"
msgid "One last secret of Old Master Luz. One we didn't uncover. Probably a last line of defense in case the world wasn't the serene place he envisioned when someone came for the seal."
msgstr "One last secret of Old Master Luz. One we didn't uncover. Probably a last line of defense in case the world wasn't the serene place he envisioned when someone came for the seal."

