msgstr "Run, mate!"

#: 906R01
msgctxt "906R01"
msgid "And that's how I was saved by the speaking statue of Memnon."
msgstr "And that's how I was saved by the speaking statue of Memnon."

#: 907R01
msgctxt "907R01"
msgid "Call it the wind or what you will. The statue spoke. Believe it or not."
msgstr "Call it the wind or what you will. The statue spoke. Believe it or not."

#: 907R02
msgctxt "907R02"
msgid "The Emerald Seal will be safer right where it is. Whatever happens in the dark days to come, it can't be used to tip the balance of power."
msgstr "The Emerald Seal will be safer right where it is. Whatever happens in the dark days to come, it can't be used to tip the balance of power."

#: 908D01
msgctxt "908D01"
msgid "If they hit the hydrogen, we're doomed!"
msgstr "If they hit the hydrogen, we're doomed!"

#: 908F01
msgctxt "908F01"
msgid "There's a sub down there! They're shooting at us!"
msgstr "There's a sub down there! They're shooting at us!"

#: 908M01
msgctxt "908M01"
msgid "Oh, Robert..."
msgstr "Oh, Robert..."

#: 908M01A
msgctxt "908M01A"
msgid "Sometimes your tails are too extravagant."
msgstr "Sometimes your tails are too extravagant."

#: 908M01B
msgctxt "908M01B"
msgid "Even for me."
msgstr "Even for me."

#: 908M02
msgctxt "908M02"
msgid "What did they want?"
msgstr "What did they want?"

#: 908M03
msgctxt "908M03"
msgid "I'm glad you escaped."
msgstr "I'm glad you escaped."

#: 908M04
msgctxt "908M04"
msgid "Life would be boring without you."
msgstr "Life would be boring without you."

#: 908M05
msgctxt "908M05"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Yes."

#: 908M05A
msgctxt "908M05A"
msgid "And New York is only a few hours away."
msgstr "And New York is only a few hours away."

#: 908M06
msgctxt "908M06"
msgid "I'm very proud of you, Robert."
msgstr "I'm very proud of you, Robert."

#: 908M07
msgctxt "908M07"
msgid "Thank you for helping my grandmother escape China."
msgstr "Thank you for helping my grandmother escape China."

#: 908M08
msgctxt "908M08"
msgid "With my aunt and uncle in London."
msgstr "With my aunt and uncle in London."

#: 908M08A
msgctxt "908M08A"
msgid "And there's no use saying you had nothing to do with it."
msgstr "And there's no use saying you had nothing to do with it."

#: 908M09
msgctxt "908M09"
msgid "You arranged it all."
msgstr "You arranged it all."

#: 908M09A
msgctxt "908M09A"
msgid "Don't try to deny it."
msgstr "Don't try to deny it."

#: 908M09B
msgctxt "908M09B"
msgid "I know everything."
msgstr "I know everything."

#: 908M10
msgctxt "908M10"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Yes."

#: 908M10A
msgctxt "908M10A"
msgid "We can forget all about that troubled world down there."
msgstr "We can forget all about that troubled world down there."

#: 908M10B
msgctxt "908M10B"
msgid "All the danger is behind us now."
msgstr "All the danger is behind us now."

#: 908R01
msgctxt "908R01"
msgid "Just the same, Mei Chen."
msgstr "Just the same, Mei Chen."

#: 908R01A
msgctxt "908R01A"
msgid "It's true."
msgstr "It's true."

#: 908R01B
msgctxt "908R01B"
msgid "I'm lucky I made it out of Egypt."
msgstr "I'm lucky I made it out of Egypt."

#: 908R02
msgctxt "908R02"
msgid "Not my autograph, old wager."
msgstr "Not my autograph, old wager."

#: 908R03
msgctxt "908R03"
msgid "We both take pleasure where we find it, May."
msgstr "We both take pleasure where we find it, May."

#: 908R03A
msgctxt "908R03A"
msgid "That's why we're so well suited to each other."
msgstr "That's why we're so well suited to each other."

#: 908R04
msgctxt "908R04"
msgid "I couldn't have done it without you, May."
msgstr "I couldn't have done it without you, May."

#: 908R05
msgctxt "908R05"
msgid "I don't know what you mean."
msgstr "I don't know what you mean."

#: 908R05A
msgctxt "908R05A"
msgid "Is she safe?"
msgstr "Is she safe?"

#: 908R06
msgctxt "908R06"
msgid "Well, I didn't think it would hurt to make inquiries."
msgstr "Well, I didn't think it would hurt to make inquiries."

#: 908R07
msgctxt "908R07"
msgid "Ah..."
msgstr "Ah..."

#: 908R07A
msgctxt "908R07A"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "What?"

#: 908R07B
msgctxt "908R07B"
msgid "Gosh."
msgstr "Gosh."

