msgstr "Any ideas?"

#: COM035
msgctxt "COM035"
msgid "I'm open to suggestion."
msgstr "I'm open to suggestion."

#: COM036
msgctxt "COM036"
msgid "I'm a little bit perplexed about what to do."
msgstr "I'm a little bit perplexed about what to do."

