msgstr "I wish I could figure out what to do next."

#: COM038
msgctxt "COM038"
msgid "Robert?"
msgstr "Robert?"

#: COM039
msgctxt "COM039"
msgid "I have faith in you."
msgstr "I have faith in you."

#: COM040
msgctxt "COM040"
msgid "You've brought us this far."
msgstr "You've brought us this far."

#: COM041
msgctxt "COM041"
msgid "Don't give up now!"
msgstr "Don't give up now!"

