msgstr "The emerald seal is almost within our grasp."

#: COM046
msgctxt "COM046"
msgid "It's been weeks, but here we are at last."
msgstr "It's been weeks, but here we are at last."

#: COM047
msgctxt "COM047"
msgid "At times I thought we'd never make it."
msgstr "At times I thought we'd never make it."

#: COM048
msgctxt "COM048"
msgid "It seems like only yesterday we were gliding peacefully along, high above the Atlantic."
msgstr "It seems like only yesterday we were gliding peacefully along, high above the Atlantic."

#: COM049
msgctxt "COM049"
msgid "When I first met you, I could tell knowing you would be an adventure."
msgstr "When I first met you, I could tell knowing you would be an adventure."

