msgstr "And he's certainly not going to let go of that spear."

#: COM072
msgctxt "COM072"
msgid "As long as the urn keeps burning, that's all I need."
msgstr "As long as the urn keeps burning, that's all I need."

#: COM073
msgctxt "COM073"
