#: COM112
msgctxt "COM112"
msgid "A coil of rope."
msgstr "A coil of rope."

#: COM112A
msgctxt "COM112A"
msgid "The rope is too short."
msgstr "The rope is too short."

#: COM113
msgctxt "COM113"
msgid "The vine is too short."
msgstr "The vine is too short."

#: COM114
msgctxt "COM114"
msgid "Even tied together, the vines are not quite long enough."
msgstr "Even tied together, the vines are not quite long enough."

#: COM115
msgctxt "COM115"
msgid "Uh-oh, there doesn't seem to be a way to turn it off."
msgstr "Uh-oh, there doesn't seem to be a way to turn it off."

#: COM116
msgctxt "COM116"
msgid "The horn is filled to the brim with water."
msgstr "The horn is filled to the brim with water."

#: COM117
msgctxt "COM117"
msgid "The pull cord has securely plugged one end of the horn."
msgstr "The pull cord has securely plugged one end of the horn."

#: COM118
msgctxt "COM118"
msgid "I don't see any reason to do that right now."
msgstr "I don't see any reason to do that right now."

#: COM119
msgctxt "COM119"
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Hmm..."

#: COM120
msgctxt "COM120"
msgid "A wooden beam."
msgstr "A wooden beam."

#: COM121
msgctxt "COM121"
msgid "A wooden post."
msgstr "A wooden post."

#: COM122
msgctxt "COM122"
msgid "May has little use for the crank right now."
msgstr "May has little use for the crank right now."

#: COM123
msgctxt "COM123"
msgid "Ripley, you removed the prayer wheel."
msgstr "Ripley, you removed the prayer wheel."

#: COM124
msgctxt "COM124"
msgid "The Romanov Emerald will make a spectacular addition to the auditorium's cartoon gallery."
msgstr "The Romanov Emerald will make a spectacular addition to the auditorium's cartoon gallery."

#: COM125
msgctxt "COM125"
msgid "Sigh..."
msgstr "Sigh..."

#: COM126
msgctxt "COM126"
msgid "I'll have to untie it first."
msgstr "I'll have to untie it first."

#: COM127
msgctxt "COM127"
msgid "An empty niche."
msgstr "An empty niche."

#: COM128
msgctxt "COM128"
msgid "I worked so hard to get that. I don't think I'll put it back."
msgstr "I worked so hard to get that. I don't think I'll put it back."

#: COM129
msgctxt "COM129"
msgid "I worked so hard to do that. I think I'll leave things the way they are."
msgstr "I worked so hard to do that. I think I'll leave things the way they are."

#: COM130
msgctxt "COM130"
msgid "A coat rack."
msgstr "A coat rack."

#: COM131
msgctxt "COM131"
msgid "Oops."
msgstr "Oops."

#: COM132
msgctxt "COM132"
msgid "The rope is tied to the end of the ladder."
msgstr "The rope is tied to the end of the ladder."

#: COM133
msgctxt "COM133"
msgid "The vine is tied to the end of the ladder."
msgstr "The vine is tied to the end of the ladder."

#: COM134
msgctxt "COM134"
msgid "The vines are tied to the end of the ladder."
msgstr "The vines are tied to the end of the ladder."

#: COM135
msgctxt "COM135"
msgid "An ancient tower of closely fitted stones."
msgstr "An ancient tower of closely fitted stones."

#: COM136
msgctxt "COM136"
msgid "It would certainly make the clay wet, but what good would that do me?"
msgstr "It would certainly make the clay wet, but what good would that do me?"

#: COM137
msgctxt "COM137"
msgid "May, wait here for a moment. I'll be right back."
msgstr "May, wait here for a moment. I'll be right back."

#: COM138
msgctxt "COM138"
msgid "It's remarkable."
msgstr "It's remarkable."

#: COM139
msgctxt "COM139"
msgid "Feng Li is not only a trusted business associate, but a dear friend as well."
msgstr "Feng Li is not only a trusted business associate, but a dear friend as well."

#: COM140
msgctxt "COM140"
msgid "I think Dr. Twelfthreeze already suspects I borrowed her pole. If she thinks I stole her lighter as well, she could have me kicked off the island. I'd better hang on to it for now."
msgstr "I think Dr. Twelfthreeze already suspects I borrowed her pole. If she thinks I stole her lighter as well, she could have me kicked off the island. I'd better hang on to it for now."

#: COM141
msgctxt "COM141"
msgid "The way the wind is gusting down the shafts the light enters through, the lighter would be next to useless."
msgstr "The way the wind is gusting down the shafts the light enters through, the lighter would be next to useless."

#: COM142
msgctxt "COM142"
msgid "Keep studying. Enlightenment is not as far away as you might think."
msgstr "Keep studying. Enlightenment is not as far away as you might think."

#: COM143
msgctxt "COM143"
msgid "Having traveled the path to enlightenment, the prayer wheels are no longer of any use to me."
msgstr "Having traveled the path to enlightenment, the prayer wheels are no longer of any use to me."

#: COM144
msgctxt "COM144"
msgid "Ripley, aimless digging will get you nowhere."
msgstr "Ripley, aimless digging will get you nowhere."

#: COM145
msgctxt "COM145"
msgid "I'd better save the lighter fluid until I really need it."
msgstr "I'd better save the lighter fluid until I really need it."

#: COM146
msgctxt "COM146"
msgid "Just out of reach."
msgstr "Just out of reach."
